title: Jacinda Ardern Is Latest New Zealander to Move to Australia
summary_full: Jacinda Ardern, New Zealand’s former leader, is basing her family in Australia “for the moment,” a spokesman said. She is part of a wave of Kiwis relocating to their larger neighbor.
